remarks.remark: Yungsook “ Yung” Kim has been a resident of Roslyn for 24 years and currently resides in Harbor View, Port Washington where she serves on the Architectural committee & Social committee. Yung emigrated from South Korea in 1964, married, and raised three children in Roslyn. She has worked as a real estate salesperson for 15 years and has listed and sold numerous houses, condominiums and apartments in Flushing, Bayside, Douglaston, little Neck, Great Neck, New Hyde Park, Manhasset, Manhasset Hills, Roslyn, Roslyn Heights, Glen Cove, Glen Head ,Brookville, Sands Point, and Port Washington.
